  "muayeneEkleSuruplukVarsayilanMesaj": "Honey flow is approaching. Feeding should be stopped to reduce sugar residue risk; feeder can be removed and frames given instead.",
  "muayeneEkleSuruplukHasatMesaj": "Honey/harvest record entered. Feeding area will reopen in the post-harvest care period; feeder can be used again if needed. When the second honey flow window opens, the same feeder removal and feeding stop cycle will run again.",
  "muayeneEkleSuruplukBildirilenKisit": "Feeding restriction started because honey flow is approaching. If you actually removed the feeder to reduce sugar residue risk, mark it.",
  "muayeneEkleBeslemeSuruplukBilgi": "Feeder marked as removed. Sugar-based feeding selection was disabled in the same inspection; this record is read as harvest preparation.",
  "muayeneEkleHasatBakimBilgi": "Feeding area reactivated because honey/harvest was entered. This period is read as post-harvest care. If the second honey flow becomes active, the system will return to feeding stop and feeder removal warnings.",
